{"title":"潜伏","authors":["黄咏梅"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":6,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"潜伏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄咏梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当披上迷彩服潜伏的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是忍耐着装点得像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵树，一块石头，或一片草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹在身边爆炸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却一动不动地伏着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一只蜕变的蝉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用痛苦等待着新的歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在硝烟里凝固"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怀疑这是安泰的化石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚毅的脸流露出石头的坚硬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是古老的巨龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾飞前的寂静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一幅静的潜伏雕塑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝成国界线每一个吉祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硝烟里这幅雕塑是一座长城"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}